        Health Data Science and Informatics", role = c("cph")) )
Maintainer: Gowtham Rao <rao@ohdsi.org>
Description: Software tool designed to compute the temporal
        relationship defined as pathways between any two instantiated
        cohorts. The cohorts are input as Target and event cohorts.
